com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.server.snomed.version

Class SnomedPublishManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.server.version.PublishManager
      • com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.server.snomed.version.SnomedPublishManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPublishManager

    public class SnomedPublishManager
extends PublishManager
    Publish manager for SNOMED CT ontology.

    This class is responsible for the followings:

    • Adjust the effective time on all unpublished SNOMED CT components and reference set members.
    • Sets the released flags on all un-released SNOMED CT components and reference set members.
    • Updates the module dependency reference set state based on the overall component changes.

      • isIgnoredType

        protected boolean isIgnoredType(org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EClass eClass)
        Since effective time and publication cannot be interpreted for SNOMED CT reference sets, we ignore them.

        Returns true if a component given with its EClass has to be ignored from the publication process. Otherwise returns with false.

        By default this method always returns with false.}
